data-triple-N3.o: "Cardiff City Football Club (Welsh: Clwb Pel-droed Dinas Caerdydd) is a professional football club based in Cardiff, Wales. The club competes in the English football league system and is currently playing in the Football League Championship. They play their home games at the Cardiff City Stadium, where they moved to in 2009 after 99 years at nearby Ninian Park. Cardiff City were founded in 1899 and they're the only club outside of England to win the FA Cup, which they won in 1927."@en
